window.bookSummaryJSON = "Best-selling historian and philosopher Will Durant devoted his entire life to studying the most significant eras, individuals, and achievements of human history. Here is a summation of Durant's work, as he presents the best of world history, from \"The One Hundred Best Books for an Education\" to \"The Ten Greatest Thinkers,\" \"The Ten Greatest Poets,\" \"The Ten Peaks of Human Progress,\" and \"Twelve Vital Dates in Human History.\" Filled with Durant's renowned wit, knowledge, and unique ability to explain events in simple and exciting terms, it is a concise liberal arts education."; 
